This code - illustration for lessons about simple Operating System creation.

Author: maisvendoo, http://phantomexos.blogspot.ru

Requirements:

1) Virtual Mashine with GRUB2 loader on HDD installed
2) gcc compiler and make utility 

To build PhantomEx kernel navigate to directory with this sources and execute

$ make

Then copy kernel file to /boot directory of your Virtual Mashine HDD

Enjoy!

maisvendoo, 15 July 2013